<TEXT>
   With the death of Emperor Hirohito today and the
ascension of Crown Prince Akihito to the Chrysanthemum Throne, here
is the new order of heirs to the throne.
   1. Crown Prince Naruhito, 28, formerly known as Prince Hiro,
eldest son of Akihito.
   2. Prince Aya, 23, second son of Akihito.
