<FIRST>r a AM-People Sub a0541 01-07 0172</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-People, Sub, a0541,0174</SECOND>
<HEAD>Eds: SUBS Stockholm-dated 1st item in rdp to recast lead, deleting
